

KAPIT

   hawak sa kamay, tangan, taban; dikit
   kapit
   hold, grasp

   Kumapit ka.
   Hold on (to something).

   Kumapit ka sa akin.
   Hold on to me.

   kapit-bahay
   (“adjacent house”)
   = neighbor

   mangangapit-bahay
   to go neighboring

   kapit-kuwarto
   coined term for “roommate”

   kapit-tuko
   “gripping like a gecko”
   clinging or holding on very tight
